msg: The eclipse .project file shouldn't be in SVN. The .project file includes the name of the eclipse project, so using the one from SVN can result in the eclipse project having a different name to the one in the .project file from SVN. Therefore, removed the .project file.
Also modified svn:ignore so .project is ignored for everyone.
